				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Group dialogs for Tiefling kids when Mol is kidnapped. Ide, Mattis, Umi (and Mirkon, if he survived the harpy attack in the grove) are planning on sneaking out and heading to Moonrise to rescue their 'boss', Mol. The player can offer to go in their place, or encourage them to go (if they go, they die)."
				}
			}
